                "description": "While lacking flashy Hollywood glamour, this area represents the essential, working history of the city's wholesale food distribution network. Operating as a wholesale distributor tucked into the industrial edges of the city, Nagatoshi Produce focuses specifically on Japanese produce and agricultural products, highlighting the vital intersection of agriculture, logistics, and the diverse local restaurant industry.",
