                "name": "Jim's Burgers",
                "description": "Representing the iconic \"Greek-owned burger stand\" culture of Southern California, Jim\u2019s is an essential part of the Eastside's car-culture history. Known for its massive portions, breakfast burritos, and charbroiled burgers, it is a quintessential 24-hour community anchor.",
