                "description": "The Vibe: Designed for the world-renowned ceramicist Glen Lukens. This is a rare industrial-residential hybrid. The studio was built specifically to accommodate Lukens' massive kilns and experimental pottery work.\n\nGazetteer Note: Unlike the hillside glass boxes, this is a more grounded, \"working-class\" modernist structure. It proves Soriano\u2019s belief that steel could be utilized for utilitarian, creative spaces just as effectively as for luxury homes.",
